## Golden Rules

1. Thin `app/**/page.tsx` — compose `features/drive/components`.
2. Drive chrome in `components/layout/`, not in `components/ui/`.
3. New drive UI under `features/drive/`.
4. Tables: `docs/TABLE_BEHAVIOR_GUIDE.md`. Drive visuals: `docs/DRIVE_UI_GUIDE.md`.
5. File icons: `FileTypeIcon` (Lucide) in `features/drive/components/file-type-icon/`.

